name: Finding Freedom
description:
It shows the emotion when we want to get freedom from our problems. The emotion is represented by two figures of women that have been entangled by snake monster and struggle to escape, gain their freedom.
This art is inspired by the story of "Timun Mas", Indonesia's cultural story and myth. A woman who is born from gold cucumber that belongs to the monster. she is raised by old lady and has to come back to monster as a food.

Size 2000x2500 px
Digital art only.
